                    </div>
                    <span>This book has never been more relevant! Given the economic challenges the past 18 months have thrown at us, the ideas in this book will revitalize your marketing plans. You'll feel a renewed enthusiasm for what you do, and how you do it. I highly recommend this book for any marcom person who's feeling the pinch of tighter budgets and seeking new and innovative ideas (that aren't really new or innovative!).</span>
                  
              
